data.description: Perfect, move-in ready home located in a gated swim and lake community! Nestled in the Lake Wildwood subdivision that's just minutes from I-475, shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. This home has been very well kept and features a spacious living area that welcomes you as you enter. The living area is adjacent to the dining room and galley kitchen that offers ample counter space for prepping, cooking, and kitchen appliances. Down the hall from the living area there are three bedrooms, two full baths, and plenty of closet space for storage. The exterior of the home features a newer privacy fence, enclosed carport, and open backyard that is mostly level with plenty of room for entertaining, outdoor activities, and includes a storage building. Don't miss this one, schedule your showing today!
